{"author":"Sunan Ibn Majah","hadith":{"hadithnumber":1570,"arabicnumber":1570,"text":"। ‘আয়িশাহ্ (রাঃ) থেকে বর্ণিত। রাসূলুল্লাহ সাল্লাল্লাহু আলাইহি ওয়াসাল্লাম কবর যিয়ারতের অনুমতি দিয়েছেন।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":6,"hadith":138}}}